commit.message:
[fix] pad messages of blocksize length before enc

Otherwise decryption can't distiguish padding from message content and
fails to unpad.

Fixes #32 Invalid padding bytes on decrypting with 0.2.2
[fix] add missing assign. when no padding required
[fix] fixed error when signed prekey id is zero
[meta] use py3.6 in travis and remove develop

[meta] update python versions in travis

add py32, py36, py37
remove py34 for now
[test] remove py34 from tox for now

[fix] update impl of gen regid and get randseq

Generate regid up to 16380 by default
Allow extended range, up to 2147483647
Fixes #28 generateRegistrationId generates unsigned 32bit values
[refact] use padding from lib, rm AESCipherV2

[refact] remove python string/bytes nonsense

All operations are to be done on bytes py3, which will be str in py2 but
that should be fine.

Merge tag '0.1.42' into develop

v0.1.42

- Migrated from pycrypto to cryptography
- Minor bug fixes
Merge branch 'no-pycrypto' of https://github.com/ju-w/python-axolotl into ju-w-no-pycrypto
Merge branch 'master' of https://github.com/adamvy/python-axolotl into adamvy-master
